title: Voter in Belarus set to give President Lukashenko a 5th term
text: RSS Feeds Voter in Belarus set to give President Lukashenko a 5th term (AP Photo/Dmitry Lovetsky). Belarusian army soldiers leave voting cabins at a polling station during presidential elections in Minsk, Belarus, Sunday, Oct. 11, 2015. (AP Photo/Dmitry Lovetsky). Belarusian army soldiers examine a candidates list with a portrait of Belarusian President Alexander Lukashenko at a polling station during presidential elections in Minsk, Belarus, Sunday, Oct. 11, 2015. (AP Photo/Sergei Grits). A Belarusian woman with her son casts a ballot at a polling station during presidential elections in Minsk, Belarus, Sunday, Oct. 11, 2015. (AP Photo/Dmitry Lovetsky). A woman reflects in a mirror as she leaves a voting cabin at a polling station during presidential elections in Minsk, Belarus, Sunday, Oct. 11, 2015.
